00:05:01.280 --> 00:05:02.060
Mother,

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:04.090
I truly don't know.

00:05:04.870 --> 00:05:06.060
As Empress,

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:08.380
you've been in the palace so long without His Majesty's favor,

00:05:08.790 --> 00:05:10.580
with no hope of heirs.

00:05:11.550 --> 00:05:15.330
I want to choose concubines for His Majesty,

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:17.330
yet he keeps saying

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.730
he must discuss it with you.

00:05:20.310 --> 00:05:21.090
What,

00:05:21.790 --> 00:05:24.210
you don't want him to take concubines?

00:05:25.480 --> 00:05:26.460
Mother, please understand.

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:27.820
I've only just returned to the palace

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:29.060
and only just heard of this.

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:30.380
So,

00:05:30.870 --> 00:05:32.330
now you know that?

00:05:36.840 --> 00:05:37.620
Yes.

00:05:37.870 --> 00:05:38.900
Rest assured, Mother,

00:05:39.310 --> 00:05:40.770
I'll help you

00:05:40.790 --> 00:05:41.850
persuade His Majesty

00:05:41.990 --> 00:05:43.170
to take more consorts

00:05:43.640 --> 00:05:45.820
and give the royal family heirs.

00:05:48.350 --> 00:05:49.290
Really?

00:05:50.430 --> 00:05:51.530
Absolutely.

00:05:57.230 --> 00:05:58.020
Your Majesty,

00:05:58.480 --> 00:06:00.210
