00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:04.850
and outstanding in looks.

00:06:05.230 --> 00:06:06.460
[Pure and Spotless]
Please look them over.

00:06:08.520 --> 00:06:09.820
You want to pick consorts for me?

00:06:10.350 --> 00:06:11.170
Exactly.

00:06:11.230 --> 00:06:11.970
Why?

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:14.210
You sit on the throne above all

00:06:14.230 --> 00:06:15.460
and should expand the harem

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:16.580
