00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:19.900
Do you even hear yourself?

00:06:21.640 --> 00:06:22.940
As Empress,

00:06:22.990 --> 00:06:24.460
it's only right that I help the Empress Dowager

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:25.820
manage the inner palace.

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:27.330
