00:14:53.280 --> 00:14:55.220
for not easing her burdens sooner.

00:14:55.880 --> 00:14:56.650
Your Majesty,

00:14:56.920 --> 00:14:59.690
you've worked so hard running the inner palace all these years.

00:15:00.280 --> 00:15:02.810
Why not leave these matters to the Empress?

00:15:03.710 --> 00:15:05.410
At your age,

00:15:05.640 --> 00:15:07.620
you deserve some peace and rest.

00:15:12.400 --> 00:15:13.340
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager,

00:15:13.430 --> 00:15:14.620
please spare me!

00:15:14.710 --> 00:15:17.020
I'll do everything you say from now on.

00:15:28.040 --> 00:15:29.020
At court this morning,

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:31.170
Grand Tutor Ling and others submitted memorials,

00:15:31.590 --> 00:15:34.410
saying a man slipped into the royal banquet

00:15:34.830 --> 00:15:36.410
and that you failed in your oversight.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:43.140
Since Xing Yiyi was your personal recommendation,

00:15:43.400 --> 00:15:44.460
with her conduct in question

00:15:44.460 --> 00:15:45.570
and her dignity lost before all,

00:15:45.950 --> 00:15:47.140
you cannot escape blame.

00:15:49.430 --> 00:15:50.290
And...

00:15:51.280 --> 00:15:52.220
Why are you stammering?

00:15:52.280 --> 00:15:53.100
Speak!

00:15:53.760 --> 00:15:55.100
Minister Xing

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:56.140
had impeached you as well.

00:15:59.760 --> 00:16:02.140
Talk about everyone kicking you when you're down.

00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:04.770
He's just trying to wash his hands clean.

00:16:05.470 --> 00:16:07.020
That old fox.

00:16:07.160 --> 00:16:08.100
Your Majesty!

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:09.020
Your Majesty!

00:16:09.160 --> 00:16:10.450
His Majesty has decreed today

00:16:10.470 --> 00:16:12.170
that the Phoenix Seal be placed in the Empress's care.

00:16:12.190 --> 00:16:12.980
They...

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:14.860
they've already taken the Phoenix Seal away.

00:16:15.160 --> 00:16:15.930
What?

00:16:23.470 --> 00:16:25.260
Satisfied now, my dear?

00:16:27.830 --> 00:16:29.410
You knew my plan from the start,

00:16:29.520 --> 00:16:30.900
that's why you chose Xing Yiyi?

00:16:30.920 --> 00:16:31.690
What else?

00:16:32.310 --> 00:16:33.340
Did you really think

00:16:33.590 --> 00:16:34.740
I actually liked her?

00:16:35.640 --> 00:16:37.100
Whether you like her is your business,

00:16:37.590 --> 00:16:38.530
nothing to do with me.

00:16:42.280 --> 00:16:42.980
I had

00:16:43.000 --> 00:16:45.190
every candidate's background thoroughly checked

00:16:45.640 --> 00:16:47.100
before settling on Xing Yiyi.

00:16:47.240 --> 00:16:48.380
Even if you hadn't picked her,

00:16:48.590 --> 00:16:49.650
I had other ways.

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:50.930
Oh?

00:16:51.830 --> 00:16:52.740
What ways?

00:16:52.950 --> 00:16:55.100
All the names I handed you were filtered by me,

00:16:55.120 --> 00:16:56.140
each with their own issues.

00:16:57.640 --> 00:16:58.500
So you're saying

00:16:59.400 --> 00:17:01.690
you never meant to choose consorts for me at all?

00:17:04.190 --> 00:17:05.540
Whether you take consorts isn't the point.

00:17:06.430 --> 00:17:07.340
What matters is

00:17:09.320 --> 00:17:11.100
I've finally got the Phoenix Seal.

00:17:19.600 --> 00:17:21.210
You care that much about the Phoenix Seal?

00:17:26.320 --> 00:17:27.410
Only with it in my hand

00:17:28.950 --> 00:17:30.730
can I do what I need to do.

00:17:39.510 --> 00:17:40.300
Your Majesty,

00:17:40.560 --> 00:17:41.580
please save me!

00:17:42.160 --> 00:17:43.170
I'm...

00:17:44.320 --> 00:17:46.210
I'm already carrying a child.

00:17:47.230 --> 00:17:48.620
You're carrying a child

00:17:48.990 --> 00:17:50.780
and still dare to dream of marrying into the throne?

00:17:51.030 --> 00:17:52.860
You insisted I enter the palace.

00:17:53.320 --> 00:17:54.540
You said back then

00:17:55.190 --> 00:17:57.900
if I came in to spy on His Majesty for you,

00:17:58.470 --> 00:18:01.170
you'd see the Xing clan rise high and smooth.

00:18:01.510 --> 00:18:02.860
That still doesn't excuse you

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:05.010
for such deceit and betrayal!

00:18:06.750 --> 00:18:07.730
Please, calm your anger.

00:18:08.600 --> 00:18:10.010
It was all my negligence.

00:18:10.230 --> 00:18:11.410
Please punish me instead.

00:18:12.510 --> 00:18:13.300
Get up.

00:18:14.030 --> 00:18:15.100
At this point,

00:18:16.030 --> 00:18:17.450
blame won't help us.

00:18:18.560 --> 00:18:19.690
It's all my fault

00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:21.970
for underestimating that Ling Cangcang.

00:18:22.470 --> 00:18:23.620
You're right.

00:18:25.270 --> 00:18:26.140
Miss Xing,

00:18:26.840 --> 00:18:28.450
we were all tricked by the Empress.

00:18:29.030 --> 00:18:30.340
She only ever meant to use you

00:18:30.360 --> 00:18:31.690
to snatch back the Phoenix Seal.

00:18:32.160 --> 00:18:34.380
She let Zhou slip in too.

00:18:35.230 --> 00:18:36.140
She's the one

00:18:36.670 --> 00:18:38.140
who drove you to this state.

00:18:46.600 --> 00:18:48.100
The Empress Dowager spared your life

00:18:49.270 --> 00:18:52.140
so you could seize this last chance.

00:18:52.800 --> 00:18:54.140
An eye for an eye,

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:56.300
a tooth for a tooth.

00:18:57.230 --> 00:18:59.340
Make the one who ruined you

00:19:00.160 --> 00:19:02.100
pay the price.

00:19:07.990 --> 00:19:08.780
Child,

00:19:09.990 --> 00:19:12.820
don't let me down again.

00:19:32.900 --> 00:19:36.820
[Linghe Hall]

00:19:42.320 --> 00:19:42.970
Your Majesty,

00:19:43.160 --> 00:19:45.900
all the Lingbi Sect files are stored in the Inner Archive.

00:19:57.710 --> 00:19:58.490
Let's go.

00:19:58.490 --> 00:20:16.140
[Inner Archive]

00:20:24.270 --> 00:20:25.900
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:20:36.640 --> 00:20:37.410
Your Majesty,

00:20:37.750 --> 00:20:40.580
there are over eighty thousand dossiers here.

00:20:40.800 --> 00:20:43.300
What you seek really won't be easy to find.

00:20:45.160 --> 00:20:46.210
Are you trying

00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:47.970
to mislead me?

00:20:50.360 --> 00:20:51.340
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:20:51.430 --> 00:20:52.540
I wouldn't dare!

00:20:52.600 --> 00:20:53.820
Then you'd better talk fast.

00:20:54.120 --> 00:20:56.620
If I report to His Majesty that you offended me,

00:20:56.640 --> 00:20:57.540
I can't guarantee

00:20:57.800 --> 00:20:58.930
you'll like the outcome.

00:21:00.270 --> 00:21:01.250
Please, don't be angry!

00:21:01.560 --> 00:21:02.650
In answer to Your Majesty,

00:21:02.880 --> 00:21:03.860
Commander Li

00:21:04.360 --> 00:21:05.450
came here yesterday

00:21:05.670 --> 00:21:07.100
and took the dossiers.

00:21:07.160 --> 00:21:08.010
He also took

00:21:08.360 --> 00:21:09.140
a...

00:21:09.670 --> 00:21:10.490
a coffin.

00:21:12.230 --> 00:21:13.100
A coffin...

00:21:15.580 --> 00:21:22.700
[Inner Archive]

00:21:32.510 --> 00:21:33.300
Your Majesty,

00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:34.730
shall we

00:21:34.990 --> 00:21:36.210
return to Linghe Hall?

00:21:36.920 --> 00:21:37.860
You may go back first.

00:21:38.160 --> 00:21:39.340
I'll walk by myself for a while.

00:21:40.230 --> 00:21:41.010
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:21:47.230 --> 00:21:48.580
Xiao Huan must have known

00:21:48.750 --> 00:21:49.970
I'd use the Phoenix Seal

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:51.650
to enter the Inner Archive.

00:21:52.320 --> 00:21:54.650
So he moved what I wanted ahead of time.

00:21:55.510 --> 00:21:56.540
And that thing

00:21:57.800 --> 00:21:58.930
is a coffin.

00:21:59.640 --> 00:22:01.580
Moon-Eclipse is the Ghost King's token

00:22:01.950 --> 00:22:03.380
and can be planted in a human heart.

00:22:03.990 --> 00:22:05.170
Perhaps, Master's body

00:22:07.270 --> 00:22:08.900
lies in that coffin,

00:22:11.360 --> 00:22:12.450
with Moon-Eclipse

00:22:14.030 --> 00:22:15.730
still inside him?

00:22:17.710 --> 00:22:18.900
What's wrong, Master?

00:22:21.230 --> 00:22:23.210
The Ghost King is dangerous.

00:22:23.400 --> 00:22:24.860
That Ghost King's committed countless atrocities

00:22:24.880 --> 00:22:25.780
and harmed so many people.

00:22:26.120 --> 00:22:26.900
None of this

00:22:27.230 --> 00:22:28.410
is something you should meddle in.

00:22:29.160 --> 00:22:30.100
Remember this:

00:22:30.840 --> 00:22:32.010
in this world,

00:22:32.430 --> 00:22:34.170
the only one who's wholly good to you

00:22:34.470 --> 00:22:35.650
is your father.

00:22:36.230 --> 00:22:37.410
Even I, your master,

00:22:37.920 --> 00:22:38.930
you mustn't trust completely.

00:22:40.710 --> 00:22:41.580
Master...

00:22:43.920 --> 00:22:45.060
are you really the Ghost King?

00:23:01.640 --> 00:23:02.490
No way...

00:23:06.080 --> 00:23:06.930
That's impossible.

00:23:14.360 --> 00:23:15.060
It was you.

00:23:15.080 --> 00:23:16.170
I'll kill you!

00:23:16.430 --> 00:23:17.250
Listen.

00:23:17.670 --> 00:23:18.860
Before you ever entered the palace,

00:23:18.880 --> 00:23:20.490
I'd already planned a way out for you.

00:23:20.800 --> 00:23:22.170
You can choose to stay,

00:23:22.470 --> 00:23:23.250
or

00:23:23.510 --> 00:23:24.540
I can send you out of the palace

00:23:24.710 --> 00:23:26.540
to live freely with the man you love.

00:23:27.230 --> 00:23:28.010
Really?

00:23:28.230 --> 00:23:29.010
Of course.

00:23:29.230 --> 00:23:30.970
That was part of my plan all along.

00:23:31.880 --> 00:23:33.250
Now that I hold the Phoenix Seal,

00:23:33.270 --> 00:23:35.250
one decree from me and no one will dare stop you leaving.

00:23:50.080 --> 00:23:53.010
They will never let you walk out of here alive.

00:23:54.840 --> 00:23:55.650
Why not?

00:23:56.750 --> 00:23:57.540
Because

00:23:59.640 --> 00:24:00.450
they

00:24:02.120 --> 00:24:03.450
want you dead!

00:24:25.470 --> 00:24:26.540
That useless girl,

00:24:26.990 --> 00:24:28.210
good for nothing

00:24:28.560 --> 00:24:29.780
and only making trouble.

00:24:30.080 --> 00:24:31.060
Please, calm your anger.

00:24:31.360 --> 00:24:32.780
At least Xing Yiyi had the sense

00:24:33.190 --> 00:24:34.620
to die at the Empress's hand.

00:24:36.190 --> 00:24:37.690
Send word to Minister Xing

00:24:37.950 --> 00:24:40.450
that the Empress punished Xing Yiyi for disrupting the harem

00:24:40.470 --> 00:24:41.690
and had her tortured to death.

00:24:41.990 --> 00:24:42.780
Yes,

00:24:42.800 --> 00:24:43.490
Your Majesty.

00:24:48.600 --> 00:24:49.900
Ling Cangcang,

00:24:50.160 --> 00:24:52.100
you little brat,

00:24:52.640 --> 00:24:54.540
how could you ever be a match for me?

00:24:55.990 --> 00:24:56.930
We'll see

00:24:57.080 --> 00:24:58.970
who comes to save you this time.

00:25:05.380 --> 00:25:08.940
[Wuying Hall]

00:25:17.600 --> 00:25:18.410
Your Majesty,

00:25:19.270 --> 00:25:20.580
Minister Xing is kneeling outside the hall,

00:25:20.670 --> 00:25:22.210
saying Xing Yiyi died miserably in the palace.

00:25:22.270 --> 00:25:23.780
He begs Your Majesty to clear her name.

00:25:26.710 --> 00:25:27.820
Send him back.

00:25:28.560 --> 00:25:29.450
Tell him

00:25:29.920 --> 00:25:31.100
I'll handle it.

00:25:31.670 --> 00:25:32.340
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:25:42.080 --> 00:25:45.010
They will never let you walk out of here alive.

00:25:45.270 --> 00:25:46.170
They

00:25:47.710 --> 00:25:48.780
want you dead!

00:25:55.750 --> 00:25:56.540
Your Majesty,

00:25:56.670 --> 00:25:57.780
Eunuch Feng is here.

00:25:59.190 --> 00:26:01.580
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:26:01.800 --> 00:26:03.210
I bear an oral decree from His Majesty.

00:26:03.470 --> 00:26:06.540
His Majesty asks you to hand over the Phoenix Seal.

00:26:08.470 --> 00:26:09.250
What?

00:26:10.120 --> 00:26:11.170
Hand over the Phoenix Seal?

00:26:11.560 --> 00:26:14.170
I'm only here to pass on His Majesty's words.

00:26:17.660 --> 00:26:21.420
[Pure and Spotless]

00:26:25.030 --> 00:26:26.540
Why must I hand over the Phoenix Seal?

00:26:28.270 --> 00:26:29.300
Do you know

00:26:30.470 --> 00:26:31.210
that these

00:26:31.510 --> 00:26:32.930
are all memorials impeaching you?

00:26:33.190 --> 00:26:35.540
This was all arranged by the Empress Dowager.

00:26:35.840 --> 00:26:37.410
She ordered Xing Yiyi to kill me,

00:26:37.840 --> 00:26:39.340
never intending to let her live.

00:26:39.470 --> 00:26:40.690
I'm well aware of that.

00:26:40.920 --> 00:26:42.140
And you still do this?

00:26:42.270 --> 00:26:43.450
This is the palace,

00:26:43.800 --> 00:26:44.900
not the martial world.

00:26:45.270 --> 00:26:47.010
The palace is an arena of power,

00:26:47.190 --> 00:26:49.410
not a place for weighing right and wrong.

00:26:49.430 --> 00:26:50.230
So Xing Yiyi dies

00:26:50.230 --> 00:26:51.820
without the truth, just like that?

00:26:53.080 --> 00:26:54.410
Is a human life

00:26:55.470 --> 00:26:57.210
nothing more than a tool to seize the Phoenix Seal?

00:26:59.750 --> 00:27:01.010
Hand over the Phoenix Seal first.

00:27:01.600 --> 00:27:02.900
When this blows over,

00:27:03.430 --> 00:27:04.930
I'll give it back to you.

00:27:05.950 --> 00:27:07.410
You want me to hand it over

00:27:08.160 --> 00:27:09.490
because they've impeached me,

00:27:09.990 --> 00:27:11.010
or you can't bear me

00:27:12.120 --> 00:27:13.620
walking freely through the palace

00:27:14.160 --> 00:27:15.650
with the Phoenix Seal?

00:27:16.470 --> 00:27:17.730
What are you implying?

00:27:18.030 --> 00:27:19.250
You know very well.

00:27:23.080 --> 00:27:26.060
I did move your master's body.

00:27:26.270 --> 00:27:27.450
I didn't want you to find it.

00:27:27.880 --> 00:27:29.010
But it was also because

00:27:29.750 --> 00:27:32.140
I didn't want you dragged into this.

00:27:34.710 --> 00:27:36.010
My Begonia Pendant glows

00:27:36.710 --> 00:27:38.170
whenever it's near poison.

00:27:38.710 --> 00:27:40.490
When it was close to my master's body,

00:27:40.510 --> 00:27:41.540
it glowed.

00:27:41.990 --> 00:27:43.730
Is it because his body

00:27:45.710 --> 00:27:47.060
was hiding Moon-Eclipse?

00:27:53.360 --> 00:27:54.860
Did you already know

00:27:56.430 --> 00:27:57.450
he was the Ghost King,

00:27:59.600 --> 00:28:01.010
and kill him for that?

00:28:01.990 --> 00:28:02.780
Cangcang,

00:28:04.430 --> 00:28:06.970
there was more to your master than just being the Ghost King.

00:28:07.750 --> 00:28:09.300
So moving his body

00:28:10.670 --> 00:28:13.250
was also to stop Moon-Eclipse from harming the world?

00:28:15.120 --> 00:28:15.900
Is that it?

00:28:20.270 --> 00:28:21.140
Answer me.

00:28:31.600 --> 00:28:32.730
I gave your master my word.

00:28:32.750 --> 00:28:34.690
He had no right to decide for me!

00:28:37.190 --> 00:28:38.170
And neither do you.

00:28:47.160 --> 00:28:47.930
Fine.

00:28:49.510 --> 00:28:51.060
I'll take you somewhere now.

00:30:17.880 --> 00:30:18.490
Master...

00:30:18.990 --> 00:30:20.170
Master...

00:30:23.750 --> 00:30:24.340
Yes.

00:30:25.360 --> 00:30:26.300
It's your master.

00:30:29.270 --> 00:30:30.490
It's my master.

00:30:53.920 --> 00:30:54.860
Master...

00:30:57.120 --> 00:30:58.930
Why did you lie to me?

00:31:01.990 --> 00:31:03.250
Why?

00:31:05.120 --> 00:31:07.220
Why are you the Ghost King?

00:31:12.750 --> 00:31:13.620
Cangcang,

00:31:15.190 --> 00:31:15.970
I killed him

00:31:16.990 --> 00:31:18.010
because I had no choice.

00:31:25.470 --> 00:31:27.250
Because he was the Ghost King,

00:31:30.560 --> 00:31:31.580
that was

00:31:33.710 --> 00:31:35.730
why you approached me from the start,

00:31:37.230 --> 00:31:38.250
used me

00:31:40.560 --> 00:31:42.100
and lied to me?

00:32:00.710 --> 00:32:02.580
You say you had no choice,

00:32:03.750 --> 00:32:05.900
tossing out those few words so lightly.

00:32:07.320 --> 00:32:08.410
But do you know

00:32:10.080 --> 00:32:11.450
that I've endured

00:32:12.560 --> 00:32:13.690
this heart-rending pain,

00:32:14.230 --> 00:32:15.300
day and night,

00:32:16.560 --> 00:32:17.970
with no relief at all?

00:32:20.800 --> 00:32:22.650
Do you think I don't hurt too?

00:32:25.120 --> 00:32:26.690
You hurt?

00:32:29.430 --> 00:32:31.340
Every time I see you sad and in pain,

00:32:32.470 --> 00:32:33.860
see you misunderstanding me,

00:32:34.260 --> 00:32:35.380
hating me,

00:32:36.160 --> 00:32:37.250
it hurts every time.

00:32:39.190 --> 00:32:39.970
Cangcang,

00:32:41.750 --> 00:32:43.210
in this position,

00:32:44.120 --> 00:32:45.100
I truly have no say

00:32:45.710 --> 00:32:47.100
most of the time.

00:32:48.750 --> 00:32:50.140
Then keep hurting.

00:32:51.750 --> 00:32:53.210
And let me go on hating you.

00:32:54.860 --> 00:32:56.740
♪Sky so vast...♪

00:32:57.030 --> 00:32:58.060
You're the one

00:32:59.080 --> 00:33:00.650
who, from the very start,

00:33:01.320 --> 00:33:03.380
only ever lied to me and used me.

00:33:04.670 --> 00:33:05.410
Cangcang,

00:33:06.400 --> 00:33:08.690
I've always been sincere with you.

00:33:10.990 --> 00:33:11.820
Sincere?

00:33:12.500 --> 00:33:14.420
♪Snow so white...♪

00:33:15.600 --> 00:33:16.860
What counts as sincerity?

00:33:18.920 --> 00:33:20.060
Even Master

00:33:22.120 --> 00:33:23.650
I was closest to and trusted most

00:33:25.080 --> 00:33:26.340
was lying to me.

00:33:29.980 --> 00:33:32.060
♪Pale moonlight...♪

00:33:32.880 --> 00:33:34.300
In this world,

00:33:34.580 --> 00:33:36.660
♪Drifting far...♪

00:33:37.320 --> 00:33:38.730
who else can I trust?

00:33:38.940 --> 00:33:41.020
♪Sword on my back♪

00:33:41.220 --> 00:33:46.060
♪I can't let go of this lingering longing...♪

00:33:47.560 --> 00:33:48.410
Master,

00:33:50.160 --> 00:33:51.300
tell me...

00:33:53.120 --> 00:33:54.490
in this world,

00:33:56.740 --> 00:33:58.340
♪Partings never paid in full...♪

00:33:58.670 --> 00:34:01.140
who can I still believe in?

00:34:10.030 --> 00:34:11.450
Tell your disciple,

00:34:13.070 --> 00:34:13.860
who

00:34:15.880 --> 00:34:17.700
can I still trust?

00:34:27.260 --> 00:34:30.620
♪A few strokes of history's ink♪

00:34:36.260 --> 00:34:40.300
♪Bury the boy I once was...♪

00:34:43.150 --> 00:34:43.930
Cangcang,

00:34:45.880 --> 00:34:47.050
believe it or not,

00:34:47.590 --> 00:34:48.660
it's up to you.

00:34:50.200 --> 00:34:51.380
But I will spend this life

00:34:52.400 --> 00:34:54.820
giving everything to shield you

00:34:55.990 --> 00:34:57.530
and keep you safe and sound.

00:34:58.900 --> 00:35:01.260
♪Singing to the vast sky♪

00:35:01.940 --> 00:35:05.260
♪As tears fall in countless lines♪

00:35:09.720 --> 00:35:10.300
Father,

00:35:10.630 --> 00:35:12.220
Cangcang saw Li Lu's body.

00:35:12.680 --> 00:35:14.660
It seems Moon-Eclipse is still in him.

00:35:15.550 --> 00:35:16.700
Other than that,

00:35:16.720 --> 00:35:18.450
what else did Cangcang find?

00:35:19.190 --> 00:35:20.010
I don't know.

00:35:21.150 --> 00:35:22.700
Sound Cangcang out for me.

00:35:22.800 --> 00:35:23.820
Find out

00:35:24.240 --> 00:35:25.300
how far she's gotten

00:35:26.400 --> 00:35:28.090
with Li Lu's case.

00:35:29.280 --> 00:35:30.050
Understood.

00:35:34.880 --> 00:35:35.660
Your Majesty.

00:35:40.320 --> 00:35:41.180
You may go.

00:35:46.950 --> 00:35:47.740
Your Majesty,

00:35:48.280 --> 00:35:50.050
Heaven rewards the diligent.

00:35:50.240 --> 00:35:53.490
Our people have finally caught something on the Empress.

00:36:04.140 --> 00:36:06.060
[Changyue Tavern]

00:36:16.420 --> 00:36:19.820
[Xijiang Moon]

00:36:23.150 --> 00:36:23.930
Cangcang.

00:36:29.990 --> 00:36:30.780
Cangcang,

00:36:31.320 --> 00:36:33.220
why not meet at the Ling Manor?

00:36:34.110 --> 00:36:35.490
Did he forbid you to go home?

00:36:38.070 --> 00:36:39.650
I just don't want to worry Father.

00:36:43.150 --> 00:36:44.010
Have a seat now.

00:36:55.590 --> 00:36:56.380
Master

00:36:57.360 --> 00:36:58.570
really was the Ghost King.

00:37:02.550 --> 00:37:03.490
If that's true,

00:37:04.030 --> 00:37:05.660
then the Sword Cottage incident wasn't a frame-up.

00:37:11.030 --> 00:37:11.970
Are you sure?

00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:15.610
I saw Master's body.

00:37:16.760 --> 00:37:18.490
Moon-Eclipse really is inside him.

00:37:18.800 --> 00:37:19.780
So Xiao Huan

00:37:20.190 --> 00:37:21.300
hid the body

00:37:21.710 --> 00:37:23.090
because of Moon-Eclipse.

00:37:23.480 --> 00:37:25.050
He only didn't want it

00:37:25.070 --> 00:37:26.570
falling into the wrong hands.

00:37:26.590 --> 00:37:27.260
Cangcang,

00:37:27.670 --> 00:37:28.980
how can you take his word for it?

00:37:29.360 --> 00:37:30.170
If you ask me,

00:37:30.400 --> 00:37:31.650
you still need to find a way

00:37:31.710 --> 00:37:33.740
to get Moon-Eclipse in your own hands.

00:37:34.670 --> 00:37:36.610
If that booklet is telling the truth,

00:37:36.920 --> 00:37:37.900
then in your pendant

00:37:38.280 --> 00:37:39.260
is Wanwei Herb,

00:37:39.760 --> 00:37:41.740
the perfect vessel for Moon-Eclipse.

00:37:47.360 --> 00:37:48.130
Cangcang,

00:37:48.510 --> 00:37:49.340
this concerns the lives

00:37:49.440 --> 00:37:50.690
of people across the land.

00:37:50.760 --> 00:37:52.010
You must think it through.

00:37:56.510 --> 00:37:57.820
You mean

00:37:58.150 --> 00:37:59.690
he covets Moon-Eclipse,

00:37:59.710 --> 00:38:00.460
rather than...?

00:38:00.480 --> 00:38:01.170
Cangcang,

00:38:02.030 --> 00:38:03.820
just because Mr. Li Lu is the Ghost King,

00:38:04.360 --> 00:38:05.860
you're going to forgive him again?

00:38:09.150 --> 00:38:10.090
I'm not.

00:38:12.280 --> 00:38:15.050
I have thought he might have had no choice about killing Master,

00:38:15.880 --> 00:38:17.300
but lying to me

00:38:17.880 --> 00:38:19.410
and using me to get close to Master,

00:38:19.430 --> 00:38:20.970
that was his own choice.

00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:23.820
I...

00:38:26.840 --> 00:38:27.820
I don't know...

00:38:29.240 --> 00:38:31.300
I don't know who I can trust anymore.

00:38:32.550 --> 00:38:34.380
Even Master lied to me.

00:38:36.320 --> 00:38:37.740
Can I trust you?

00:38:40.550 --> 00:38:41.970
You've never lied to me,

00:38:41.990 --> 00:38:43.180
right, Luo?

00:38:52.510 --> 00:38:53.490
Of course not.

00:38:54.280 --> 00:38:54.970
Cangcang,

00:38:55.630 --> 00:38:56.660
have you forgotten?

00:38:57.200 --> 00:38:57.970
My life

00:38:58.280 --> 00:38:59.570
was saved by you and Father.

00:39:00.110 --> 00:39:01.300
How could I ever lie to you?

00:39:09.430 --> 00:39:10.660
How is Father?

00:39:11.920 --> 00:39:12.860
Aside from worrying

00:39:13.430 --> 00:39:15.220
that you're being bullied in the palace,

00:39:15.430 --> 00:39:16.340
he's fine.

00:39:21.950 --> 00:39:23.780
At least I still have you and Father.

00:39:32.510 --> 00:39:33.050
Cangcang,

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:34.970
even if Father keeps saying

00:39:35.200 --> 00:39:36.660
you should hold tight to the Empress's seat,

00:39:37.070 --> 00:39:38.490
you must think it through.

00:39:39.550 --> 00:39:41.490
Remember how he tricked you in Southern Chu

00:39:41.510 --> 00:39:42.340
and used you.

00:39:42.920 --> 00:39:44.700
Don't let him cloud your judgment again.

00:39:50.030 --> 00:39:50.860
Here we are!

00:39:50.880 --> 00:39:51.490
Come with me!

00:39:51.510 --> 00:39:52.090
Yes!

00:39:57.430 --> 00:39:58.050
Find them!

00:40:01.720 --> 00:40:02.610
Officers...

00:40:03.880 --> 00:40:05.050
Aunt Chan?

00:40:05.760 --> 00:40:07.780
Palace guards on royal orders!

00:40:09.280 --> 00:40:10.700
How did she find this place?

00:40:23.400 --> 00:40:24.490
Your Majesty,

00:40:24.840 --> 00:40:26.860
the Empress Dowager heard you left the palace without leave

00:40:27.110 --> 00:40:28.490
and sent this maid

00:40:28.880 --> 00:40:30.570
to remind you of the rules.

00:40:35.240 --> 00:40:37.170
I brought the Empress out to drink tea.

00:40:37.800 --> 00:40:38.570
Do I now

00:40:38.990 --> 00:40:41.130
need the Empress Dowager's permission as well?

00:40:43.590 --> 00:40:44.490
This maid deserves death!

00:40:45.070 --> 00:40:46.010
This maid deserves death!

00:40:46.510 --> 00:40:48.490
For disturbing our pleasant outing,

00:40:48.880 --> 00:40:50.010
you certainly do.

00:40:51.070 --> 00:40:52.300
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:40:52.590 --> 00:40:53.530
Forgive me, Your Majesty...

00:40:53.550 --> 00:40:54.180
Get lost!

00:40:54.630 --> 00:40:55.970
I'll deal with your offense back at the palace.

00:40:56.200 --> 00:40:56.970
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:41:24.760 --> 00:41:26.010
Why did you come here?

00:41:28.110 --> 00:41:28.970
I heard Aunt Chan

00:41:28.990 --> 00:41:30.660
had brought guards here

00:41:30.720 --> 00:41:32.300
and came out of curiosity.

00:41:32.590 --> 00:41:33.300
I didn't expect

00:41:33.840 --> 00:41:34.820
to run into you.

00:41:36.840 --> 00:41:38.380
Their tea and snacks are good.

00:41:38.950 --> 00:41:39.820
I came to try them.

00:41:44.880 --> 00:41:45.970
Drinking tea alone,

00:41:46.720 --> 00:41:47.660
yet two cups on the table?

00:41:50.920 --> 00:41:53.050
Since you know I'm not here alone,

00:41:53.360 --> 00:41:54.780
why cover for me?

00:41:56.880 --> 00:41:57.780
I told you

00:41:58.200 --> 00:41:59.340
I'd keep you safe.

00:42:10.360 --> 00:42:11.130
Since I'm rarely

00:42:11.360 --> 00:42:12.490
out of the palace incognito,

00:42:13.240 --> 00:42:16.260
why not stroll around with me?

00:42:20.520 --> 00:42:21.580
Watch this!

00:42:25.260 --> 00:42:26.210
Look at that!

00:42:28.530 --> 00:42:29.860
Lanterns!

00:42:30.560 --> 00:42:31.680
Lanterns!

00:42:32.920 --> 00:42:33.800
[Lanterns]
Take a look, miss.

00:42:38.680 --> 00:42:39.410
Fireworks!

00:42:40.880 --> 00:42:41.700
Honey puffs!

00:42:41.760 --> 00:42:43.490
Fresh honey puffs!

00:42:44.200 --> 00:42:45.180
Try before you buy!

00:42:45.200 --> 00:42:46.780
Cheap and tasty!

00:42:46.990 --> 00:42:48.090
These are from our Yuan family,

00:42:48.110 --> 00:42:49.610
[Yuan's Honey Cake Shop]
made with our secret recipe!

00:42:49.630 --> 00:42:50.860
Come have a taste!

00:42:51.030 --> 00:42:52.600
Honey puffs!

00:42:52.770 --> 00:42:54.010
Come on, sir, have a bite!

00:42:55.320 --> 00:42:55.780
Sir,

00:42:56.360 --> 00:42:57.410
one serving of honey puffs.

00:42:57.430 --> 00:42:57.970
Got it.

00:42:57.970 --> 00:42:59.300
Pack one piece separately for me.

00:42:59.320 --> 00:42:59.780
Sure.

00:43:02.400 --> 00:43:03.180
- Please try it. - All right.

00:43:05.150 --> 00:43:05.930
Come catch me!

00:43:06.510 --> 00:43:06.860
Here.

00:43:07.070 --> 00:43:07.820
Have a taste.

00:43:12.550 --> 00:43:13.010
All right.

00:43:13.880 --> 00:43:14.570
Thank you.

00:43:15.240 --> 00:43:15.970
You're too kind, sir.

00:43:15.990 --> 00:43:16.740
So sweet.

00:43:18.920 --> 00:43:21.050
This was my favorite treat as a child.

00:43:22.320 --> 00:43:23.090
Why?

00:43:25.630 --> 00:43:27.090
I had a cold sickness growing up.

00:43:28.400 --> 00:43:29.660
When my mother was alive,

00:43:30.070 --> 00:43:31.300
every time she gave me medicine,

00:43:31.680 --> 00:43:33.130
she'd give me a piece of honey puff too.

00:43:33.510 --> 00:43:34.740
No matter how bitter the medicine was,

00:43:35.320 --> 00:43:36.490
as long as there was honey puff,

00:43:36.760 --> 00:43:38.860
all I could taste was sweetness.

00:43:39.920 --> 00:43:42.820
But I've hardly ever seen it in the palace.

00:43:44.840 --> 00:43:46.180
After my mother died,

00:43:46.400 --> 00:43:47.780
I swore off sweets.

00:43:48.430 --> 00:43:50.610
I wanted to remember that bitterness

00:43:50.800 --> 00:43:51.930
and remind myself

00:43:52.200 --> 00:43:53.410
never to slack off.

00:43:55.360 --> 00:43:56.130
But later,

00:43:56.680 --> 00:43:58.090
when I tasted your pear blossom honey,

00:43:58.240 --> 00:43:59.050
I realized

00:43:59.630 --> 00:44:00.410
sweetness

00:44:01.110 --> 00:44:02.380
still beats bitterness after all.

